  "phrases": [
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p01",
      "text": "This is Support Tickets, the queue your team works inside WashCentral.",
      "startS": 0,
      "endS": 4.152,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p02",
      "text": "It's the platform's own help desk, separate from the cross-customer view in the last lesson.",
      "startS": 4.606,
      "endS": 9.37,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p03",
      "text": "Everything about the day's support load lives on this one screen.",
      "startS": 9.81,
      "endS": 13.28,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p04",
      "text": "Start at the top.",
      "startS": 13.68,
      "endS": 14.564,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p05",
      "text": "Four counters frame the backlog before you read a single row:",
      "startS": 15.3,
      "endS": 18.596,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p06",
      "text": "what's open, what's in progress, what closed today,",
      "startS": 19.111,
      "endS": 22.384,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p07",
      "text": "and how long the average ticket takes to resolve.",
      "startS": 22.67,
      "endS": 25.166,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p08",
      "text": "One look tells you whether the queue is calm or backed up.",
      "startS": 26.056,
      "endS": 29.184,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p09",
      "text": "Now the left panel.",
      "startS": 29.6,
      "endS": 30.814,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p10",
      "text": "This is the twelve-month trend, not today's numbers.",
      "startS": 31.201,
      "endS": 34.265,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p11",
      "text": "Volume is climbing, up seven percent over the year.",
      "startS": 34.778,
      "endS": 37.842,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p12",
      "text": "Handy context when a client asks whether their run of issues is unusual.",
      "startS": 38.337,
      "endS": 42.197,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p13",
      "text": "The middle panel breaks tickets down by type.",
      "startS": 42.64,
      "endS": 45.075,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p14",
      "text": "Billing leads, then technical, then feedback and general.",
      "startS": 45.521,
      "endS": 47.492,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p15",
      "text": "When you're deciding where the team's hours go,",
      "startS": 47.695,
      "endS": 49.178,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p16",
      "text": "this is the split that says billing questions are the heaviest load right now.",
      "startS": 49.834,
      "endS": 55.52,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p17",
      "text": "On the right, the health panel.",
      "startS": 55.979,
      "endS": 57.482,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p18",
      "text": "Most of the queue is already resolved, a smaller share in progress, and a thin band still open.",
      "startS": 58.693,
      "endS": 64.164,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p19",
      "text": "Read across, it's a quick pulse on whether work is getting closed or piling up.",
      "startS": 64.608,
      "endS": 68.924,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p20",
      "text": "Below the summary sits the list itself.",
      "startS": 69.44,
      "endS": 71.787,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p21",
      "text": "This is where you actually work.",
      "startS": 72.274,
      "endS": 74.013,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p22",
      "text": "Two buttons ride the top corner:",
      "startS": 74.783,
      "endS": 76.399,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p23",
      "text": "one opens a brand-new ticket, the other exports the list.",
      "startS": 76.885,
      "endS": 80.466,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p24",
      "text": "We'll open a new one shortly.",
      "startS": 80.877,
      "endS": 82.265,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p25",
      "text": "We never export while recording.",
      "startS": 82.658,
      "endS": 84.64,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p26",
      "text": "Above the table, a search box and a filter control.",
      "startS": 85.131,
      "endS": 87.936,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p27",
      "text": "Type a ticket number or a few words of the subject to jump straight to it,",
      "startS": 88.602,
      "endS": 92.31,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p28",
      "text": "or open the filters to narrow by field.",
      "startS": 92.647,
      "endS": 94.811,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p29",
      "text": "On a busy queue, this is how you find one ticket fast.",
      "startS": 95.665,
      "endS": 98.99,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p30",
      "text": "Read the column headers.",
      "startS": 99.44,
      "endS": 100.89,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p31",
      "text": "Ticket number, subject, location, priority, status, owner, and created date.",
      "startS": 101.897,
      "endS": 102.644,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p32",
      "text": "The two you'll lean on most are priority, for what to grab first,",
      "startS": 102.935,
      "endS": 105.516,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p33",
      "text": "and the owner, for who already has it.",
      "startS": 105.809,
      "endS": 115.129,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p34",
      "text": "Now the rows.",
      "startS": 115.6,
      "endS": 116.829,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p35",
      "text": "A POS receipt problem in progress, a billing dispute still open,",
      "startS": 117.472,
      "endS": 119.759,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p36",
      "text": "a membership that won't activate, a tunnel emergency-stop already resolved.",
      "startS": 120.161,
      "endS": 121.892,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p37",
      "text": "Priority runs from critical down to medium,",
      "startS": 122.302,
      "endS": 124.051,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p38",
      "text": "and each ticket names a person or a team on the hook for it.",
      "startS": 124.449,
      "endS": 133.927,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p39",
      "text": "At the foot of the list, the page controls.",
      "startS": 134.4,
      "endS": 136.646,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p40",
      "text": "Rows per page, a simple counter, and pager arrows.",
      "startS": 137.018,
      "endS": 140.693,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p41",
      "text": "One quirk worth knowing: the card says eighteen records while only four load here.",
      "startS": 141.099,
      "endS": 145.944,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p42",
      "text": "In the demo tenant, treat those four as samples and the counts as stand-ins.",
      "startS": 146.322,
      "endS": 150.594,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p43",
      "text": "Now open a new ticket.",
      "startS": 151.04,
      "endS": 152.509,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p44",
      "text": "This is the one write action in the lesson.",
      "startS": 153.173,
      "endS": 155.363,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p45",
      "text": "Open the blank form, look it over, then back out without saving and without touching a field.",
      "startS": 155.585,
      "endS": 160.984,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p46",
      "text": "We're documenting where a new ticket starts, not filing one.",
      "startS": 161.294,
      "endS": 164.834,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p47",
      "text": "That's the whole page.",
      "startS": 165.359,
      "endS": 166.443,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p48",
      "text": "The counters give you the backlog,",
      "startS": 167.039,
      "endS": 168.651,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p49",
      "text": "the middle panels tell you what kind of work it is and how much is cleared,",
      "startS": 169.05,
      "endS": 172.661,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p50",
      "text": "and the list hands you each ticket with its priority and its owner.",
      "startS": 173.223,
      "endS": 176.79,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p51",
      "text": "Enough to triage before you open a single one.",
      "startS": 177.331,
      "endS": 180.16,
      "timing": "silence"
    }
  ]
